description:
Please read the description!

We are giving away all METACUBES still open from our Soonaverse Sale. 

Everyone who follows our Space and claims this award will get the chance (Whitelist) to win one of the remaining 500+ METACUBE NFT's. 

We wish all participants the best of luck.

The winners will be randomly selected from the award participants and their Soonaverse names will be published on Twitter in several posts week by week once all award's have been claimed. 


Important: 
The participation of this award requires the existence of an IOTA address with at least 1 MIOTA (Dust Protection)! This fee will be returned after a successful transaction. 

As soon as a winner is announced via twitter he has the chance to claim his NFT. If the winner does not claim his prize within 30 days, his prize will be forfeited and given to one of the other participants.
name: The Big Cube - METACUBES  Giveaway
